//                     parser written FROM SCRATCH because no Lua parser
//                     library was small enough to justify the dependency.
//                     Parses Pandemic's animation Lua scripts, renders them
//                     as an editable tree, regenerates valid Lua on save.
// Lines  2100-2300:   Lua syntax highlighter (keyword coloring, line numbers)
// Lines  2300-2530:   Bone hierarchy renderer, gamemode mask widgets
// Lines  2530-3560:   NeuralRTT_Render3D() — the 1000-line neural network
//                     D3D9 render function with 6 shader passes, instanced
//                     sphere rendering, tube rendering, bloom, SSAO, fog.
//                     This function alone is bigger than most people's
//                     entire projects. It lives inside a UI DLL. I am
