// Lines  3560-3700:   C ABI exports (Init, Shutdown, WndProc, NewFrame)
// Lines  3700-3970:   Viewport window (render-to-texture 3D view in ImGui)
// Lines  3970-20640:  ImGuiGlue_DrawFrame(). THE BIG ONE.
//                     SIXTEEN THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED AND SIXTY-EIGHT LINES.
//                     IN ONE FUNCTION. This single function draws:
//                     - Menu bar + toolbar
//                     - Model browser panel
//                     - Level panel (5000+ entity tree with hierarchy)
